{"tid":348991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇打羽毛球既巴絲?","createTime":"2017-08-06T07:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T04:10:18.000Z","uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48ca258640f4de7b007d40a9e29bb28244e1c949","tid":348991,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T07:48:31.000Z","msg":"連登有冇打羽毛球既巴絲呀?<br />\n入黎傾下計呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似冇咩post傾羽毛球, 關於羽毛球既野都可以係度傾下架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開下話題先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下你地平時有冇出去學波?<br />\n有學既話模式係點?<br />\n私人教練一對一果D定係join球會/訓練班一班人一齊打?<br />\n有時都想學下打波但唔知點開始/點樣學先至岩自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家有時都只係同D朋友好hea咁玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2827a476f7ce88fde53d8155fcd9c9ade848e4e","tid":348991,"uid":43428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T07:56:10.000Z","msg":"羽毛球腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4afb2ac01e54ef8dccbeaa3faf7de631c70ef10","tid":348991,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:41:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>羽毛球腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHello巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打平時有冇係出面學波呀?<br />\n定係同朋友打?"},{"pid":"63ee230a7058e6cc0f4a296f6362b38676aa5b2b","tid":348991,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:51:02.000Z","msg":"你為咗咩想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766e89f830e016554f59db90c4c365cb9d1060c1","tid":348991,"uid":126981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,