s/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正我點都想練體能同重訓"},{"pid":"acb601dec7cccd2f643ffeb427480abef3a6a791","tid":348991,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟最近想針對羽毛球做重訓 有冇巴打可以指導下？<br />\n因為打波成日都係體能問題而玩控制 打法多拉吊 冇乜進攻能力 所以想練核心同腳（四頭肌）<br />\n利申：球齡1年半 但睇波睇左5年 最初係2014年俾松榚吸引而開始睇 而家哂都睇</blockquote><br />\n拉吊控制更需要體能wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打點 我冇乜點跑動 我唔跳殺 唔搶攻 打被動 可能對手級數未到位 同埋同親朋友打 佢地都係猛攻型 相對黎講我體力流失得冇咁快  我打多拍 但感覺還好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正我點都想練體能同重訓</blockquote><br />\n練Core做plank<br />\n練體能就跑步<br />\n練腳就走步法"},{"pid":"0491c57524082ad52fa5ef14768c45b5a683a58a","tid":348991,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:09:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟最近想針對羽毛球做重訓 有冇巴打可以指導下？<br />\n因為打波成日都係體能問題而玩控制 打法多拉吊 冇乜進攻能力 所以想練核心同腳（四頭肌）<br />\n利申：球齡1年半 但睇波睇左5年 最初係2014年俾松榚吸引而開始睇 而家哂都睇</blockquote><br />\n拉吊控制更需要體能wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打點 我冇乜點跑動 我唔跳殺 唔搶攻 打被動 可能對手級數未到位 同埋同親朋友打 佢地都係猛攻型 相對黎講我體力流失得冇咁快  我打多拍 但感覺還好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正我點都想練體能同重訓</blockquote><br />\n練Core做plank<br />\n練體能就跑步<br />\n練腳就走步法</blockquote><br />\n手同胸呢<br />\n一排冇打 後場打後場都有難度<br />\n利申 天生體能弱 工作與體力無關"},{"pid":"d6cd5faabd122243a68e87ce83db51f804569d22","tid":348991,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:37:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟最近想針對羽毛球做重訓 有冇巴打可以指導下？<br />\n因為打波成日都係體能問題而玩控制 打法多拉吊 冇乜進攻能力 所以想練核心同腳（四頭肌）<br />\n利申：球齡1年半 但睇波睇左5年 最初係2014年俾松榚吸引而開始睇 而家哂都睇</blockquote><br />\n拉吊控制更需要體能wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打點 我冇乜點跑動 我唔跳殺 唔搶攻 打被動 可能對手級數未到位 同埋同親朋友打 佢地都係猛攻型 相對黎講我體力流失得冇咁快  我打多拍 但感覺還好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正我點都想練體能同重訓</blockquote><br />\n練Core做plank<br />\n練體能就跑步<br />\n練腳就走步法</blockquote><br />\n手同胸呢<br />\n一排冇打 後場打後場都有難度<br />\n利申 天生體能弱 工作與體力無關</blockquote><br />\n猜高遠球都有難度既話，問題應該在於動作"},{"pid":"aeeaf715ce28915f4d6494597cdb4b53b342f892","tid":348991,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:59:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>私鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打/巴打一路有打開私鐘?<br />\n係咪打到好勁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n唔勁啦<br />\n都唔係由細打起</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係幾時開始打?<br />\n打私鐘打左幾耐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n中學先開始打，但係到依家出黎做野先私鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中學果陣打校隊?<br />\n私鐘幾錢係咪好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n一對一咁睇住你邊度做得唔好就練果樣咁?</blockquote><br />\n有平有貴啦<br />\n最雞果d大約收$150一個鐘<br />\n聽過最貴就王晨收$1000一個鐘<br />\n初階會教動作，步法<br />\n到中階d就會練多球，練下控球同埋球路<br />\n之後就會練速度同力量</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮撚想學波都要諗下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n練多球應該幾重要<br />\n動作步法都話可以上網睇片自學<br />\n(雖然都可能會跟錯而自己唔知)<br />\n但多球真係一定要落場打先練到"},{"pid":"1da7139ddfb3a4f799ef4ecdb402a504c529de33","tid":348991,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我 所有賽事都會睇<br />\n最近買左松友美佐紀支拍俾女朋友<br />\n自己打開男雙<br />\n一直都想係香港搵討論區好似台灣個羽球共和國咁有規模 可惜香港唔多人鐘意羽毛球</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女朋友都有打開波?<br />\n咁幾好呀你地拍拖多樣玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港成個運動風氣都好似冇人地咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cb31794cc5e0d4439cd5993850cc3b8eefdb42","tid":348991,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:09:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟最近想針對羽毛球做重訓 有冇巴打可以指導下？<br />\n因為打波成日都係體能問題而玩控制 打法多拉吊 冇乜進攻能力 所以想練核心同腳（四頭肌）<br />\n利申：球齡1年半 但睇波睇左5年 最初係2014年俾松榚吸引而開始睇 而家哂都睇</blockquote><br />\n多啲練殺波上網、步法<br />\n你睇咁多波可以諗番人地點樣打同鋪排為自己制造一個進攻機會<br />\n如果你打拉吊 可能搵唔啱timing轉/搶攻姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇黎高手黎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f65bd1aea04c1ab2db5189d727ad94f5d8d2cc","tid":348991,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開個telegram group? BTW大家係大概咩lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/250881/page/6?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/250881/page/6?ref=android</a><br />\n隔離post有巴打開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家係咪都入左去入面個group呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71ebeabab8466dab3d323701fc7aeb3ea51245a","tid":348991,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:20:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開個telegram group? BTW大家係大概咩lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打過重點青年軍 join 唔join得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重點青年軍好勁啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱畢業？港島區？</blockquote><br />\n唔勁啦 天外有天<br />\n起碼幾年冇渣過塊拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係<br />\n九龍</blockquote><br />\n做乜唔繼續打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重青之後再上就係港青？</blockquote><br />\n制度同自身問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔緊要我學校都有兩個前重點青年軍<br />\n又係升唔到上去港青，但係都好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多高手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我試過同我教練其中一個學生重青打<br />\n輕鬆秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我打法唔跟系統<br />\n玩得太多假動作 被人話唔認真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同遲發育 就算十二歲被教練推薦去重青<br />\n去試訓對面高我個幾頭 被人問係咪黎錯<br />\n成個人灰晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e2a06fff5c998057c0d89209d8196536cddf62","tid":348991,"uid":132780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"我打開男雙，最近想搵隊唔介意一齊練，目標C-D grade（利申：得男雙D grade)，因為感覺出面打開波同真正男雙比賽差好遠，幾乎都唔升波平抽擋控網鬥頭三板，自己同partner都想再進步，有冇巴打想一齊練？"},{"pid":"fa7dd81dc3dcb4924de0d6dff0aed4c770e20c63","tid":348991,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:22:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開個telegram group? BTW大家係大概咩lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/250881/page/6?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/250881/page/6?ref=android</a><br />\n隔離post有巴打開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家係咪都入左去入面個group呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我入左個group啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都入左去既可唔可以講返邊個先係你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b94386a5c1dcd259d3fe8a9ee46ca3b2c9d48fe","tid":348991,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果book到場 星期六日 可以join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢排星期六日無波打 <br />\n利申沙田區,不過可以出九龍打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係沙田區喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望搵到多D人出黎交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就跟大家學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03b30483ac74d1cf677efee0a14c1980cf8615f","tid":348991,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我打開男雙，最近想搵隊唔介意一齊練，目標C-D grade（利申：得男雙D grade)，因為感覺出面打開波同真正男雙比賽差好遠，幾乎都唔升波平抽擋控網鬥頭三板，自己同partner都想再進步，有冇巴打想一齊練？</blockquote><br />\n打開邊區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236e045751d83919b0b8c58eb9377156418aad3e","tid":348991,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>私鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打/巴打一路有打開私鐘?<br />\n係咪打到好勁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n唔勁啦<br />\n都唔係由細打起</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係幾時開始打?<br />\n打私鐘打左幾耐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n中學先開始打，但係到依家出黎做野先私鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中學果陣打校隊?<br />\n私鐘幾錢係咪好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n一對一咁睇住你邊度做得唔好就練果樣咁?</blockquote><br />\n有平有貴啦<br />\n最雞果d大約收$150一個鐘<br />\n聽過最貴就王晨收$1000一個鐘<br />\n初階會教動作，步法<br />\n到中階d就會練多球，練下控球同埋球路<br />\n之後就會練速度同力量</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮撚想學波都要諗下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n練多球應該幾重要<br />\n動作步法都話可以上網睇片自學<br />\n(雖然都可能會跟錯而自己唔知)<br />\n但多球真係一定要落場打先練到</blockquote><br />\n步法都可以自學，動作最好有人執<br />\n因為就咁揮拍做到唔代表擊球果陣做到"},{"pid":"510fabc880dd75fd854494619e841900fee40a5e","tid":348991,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:29:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>私鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打/巴打一路有打開私鐘?<br />\n係咪打到好勁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n唔勁啦<br />\n都唔係由細打起</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係幾時開始打?<br />\n打私鐘打左幾耐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n中學先開始打，但係到依家出黎做野先私鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中學果陣打校隊?<br />\n私鐘幾錢係咪好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n一對一咁睇住你邊度做得唔好就練果樣咁?</blockquote><br />\n有平有貴啦<br />\n最雞果d大約收$150一個鐘<br />\n聽過最貴就王晨收$1000一個鐘<br />\n初階會教動作，步法<br />\n到中階d就會練多球，練下控球同埋球路<br />\n之後就會練速度同力量</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮撚想學波都要諗下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n練多球應該幾重要<br />\n動作步法都話可以上網睇片自學<br />\n(雖然都可能會跟錯而自己唔知)<br />\n但多球真係一定要落場打先練到</blockquote><br />\n步法都可以自學，動作最好有人執<br />\n因為就咁揮拍做到唔代表擊球果陣做到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以都係有人跟下執下動作會好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffca45ff672178f6f0b812caa8ab4541319b0522","tid":348991,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟最近想針對羽毛球做重訓 有冇巴打可以指導下？<br />\n因為打波成日都係體能問題而玩控制 打法多拉吊 冇乜進攻能力 所以想練核心同腳（四頭肌）<br />\n利申：球齡1年半 但睇波睇左5年 最初係2014年俾松榚吸引而開始睇 而家哂都睇</blockquote><br />\n拉吊控制更需要體能wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打點 我冇乜點跑動 我唔跳殺 唔搶攻 打被動 可能對手級數未到位 同埋同親朋友打 佢地都係猛攻型 相對黎講我體力流失得冇咁快  我打多拍 但感覺還好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正我點都想練體能同重訓</blockquote><br />\n練Core做plank<br />\n練體能就跑步<br />\n練腳就走步法</blockquote><br />\n猛攻都打倒多球 應該唔猛得去邊<br />\n搵個教練私鐘 包保你一個鐘後想打多拍都打唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da80dc917b1b1ce615486510409f21da69978b21","tid":348991,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我打開男雙，最近想搵隊唔介意一齊練，目標C-D grade（利申：得男雙D grade)，因為感覺出面打開波同真正男雙比賽差好遠，幾乎都唔升波平抽擋控網鬥頭三板，自己同partner都想再進步，有冇巴打想一齊練？</blockquote><br />\n打開邊區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n練好開波 進攻同走位夠做啦<br />\n默契如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d99f989b52c833ba626c5f7408d6d0a6c9627f","tid":348991,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係幾時開始打?<br />\n打私鐘打左幾耐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n中學先開始打，但係到依家出黎做野先私鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中學果陣打校隊?